WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.988
Sine-set ng CSS property
na box-sizing kung paano

00:00:03.012 --> 00:00:06.012
kina-calculate ang total na
width at height ng isang element.

00:00:06.036 --> 00:00:08.036
May dalawa itong values:

00:00:08.060 --> 00:00:10.060
ang border-box at content-box.

00:00:11.387 --> 00:00:14.387
Bago natin tingnan ang effects
ng dalawang values na ito,

00:00:14.411 --> 00:00:16.411
kailangan nating tandaan na lahat ng

00:00:16.435 --> 00:00:18.435
HTML elements ay mga box,

00:00:18.459 --> 00:00:20.459
kahit ano pa ang hitsura nito visually.

00:00:20.783 --> 00:00:23.583
Lahat ng HTML elements ay may margin,

00:00:23.607 --> 00:00:26.007
border, padding,

00:00:26.031 --> 00:00:28.031
at content.

00:00:28.055 --> 00:00:31.055
content-box ang default
value ng box-sizing.

00:00:31.079 --> 00:00:34.779
Kapag content-box ang
value ng box-sizing property,

00:00:34.803 --> 00:00:38.603
kina-calculate ang height at width
nang hindi kasama ang padding at border.

00:00:38.627 --> 00:00:43.327
Halimbawa, kapag nag-set ka
ng width: 100px sa isang element,

00:00:43.351 --> 00:00:45.351
hindi kasama sa 100 pixels na ito

00:00:45.375 --> 00:00:47.375
ang size ng padding at border.

00:00:47.799 --> 00:00:50.199
Kung may padding na 20 pixels ang element

00:00:50.223 --> 00:00:52.023
at border na 2 pixels,

00:00:52.047 --> 00:00:56.047
ang actual na magiging
width ng element ay 122 pixels.

00:00:57.171 --> 00:01:00.171
Kadalasan, hindi ito ang
behavior na gusto mong mangyari.

00:01:00.195 --> 00:01:04.895
Para ma-disable ito, i-set ang
box-sizing property to border-box.

00:01:04.919 --> 00:01:06.519
Sa value na ito,

00:01:06.643 --> 00:01:08.643
kasama na sa 100 pixels na width ang size

00:01:08.667 --> 00:01:10.667
ng padding at border.